QuestData.Title: Oomlot Dealt With
QuestData.Description: $n, you have to get back to the Town-In-A-Box and warn them about the goblin zombies up in the volcano's caldera!
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with Sassy Hardwrench at the Town-In-A-Box on the Lost Isles.
QuestData.RewardText: They turned some of our people into zombies? Tell me something I don't know....
